'''埃及航空804號班機'''（MS804/MSR804）是埃及航空的定期國際航線班機，是法國巴黎至埃及開羅的航班代號。2016年5月18日執飛的航班在[[欧洲东部时间|歐洲東部時間]]2016年5月19日2時45分從雷達上消失。當時，該航班已進入埃及空域約130公里處，飛行高度為37,000英呎（約11,000公尺）。隨後埃及民航局官員稱目前已經有理由相信在地中海失去聯絡的飛機已經在[[希腊|希臘]][[喀帕苏斯岛|喀帕蘇斯島]]附近墜毀<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-36309492 |title = EgyptAir flight MS804 from Paris to Cairo crashed - Hollande |date = 2016-05-19 |publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] |accessdate = 2016-05-19 |archive-date = 2021-01-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210107062319/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-36309492 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/egyptair-flight-ms804-missing-passenger-jet-has-crashed-into-the-mediterranean-sea-officials-confirm-a7037146.html |title = EgyptAir flight MS804 crash: Military searching for wreckage in Mediterranean Sea, officials say |author = Lizzie Dearden |date = 2016-05-19 |publisher = The Independent |accessdate = 2016-05-19 |archive-date = 2016-05-20 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160520121845/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/egyptair-flight-ms804-missing-passenger-jet-has-crashed-into-the-mediterranean-sea-officials-confirm-a7037146.html |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/egyptair-flight-ms804-missing-live-8003059 |title = Egyptair flight MS804 missing: live updates as plane crash with 66 on board 'almost certainly caused by attack' |author = Natalie Evans |date = 2016-05-19 |publisher = [[每日鏡報|每日鏡報網]] |accessdate = 2016-05-19 |language = en-gb |archive-date = 2016-05-19 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160519091110/http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/egyptair-flight-ms804-missing-live-8003059 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[法國航空事故調查處|法國航空事故調查處]]的調查結果認定該事故肇因為機師於駕駛艙內吸菸引燃駕駛艙氧氣面罩漏出的氧氣。

== 失事班机情况 ==
涉事飛機的型號為[[空中巴士A320系列|空中巴士A320-232]]，[[機身編號|機身編號]]為SU-GCC，使用IAE V2527-A5引擎，於2003年7月25日進行試飛並於同年11月3日交由埃及航空營運<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.airfleets.net/ficheapp/plane-a320-2088.htm |title=EgyptAir SU-GCC |publisher=Airfleets.net |accessdate=2016-05-19 |archive-date=2020-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804031409/https://www.airfleets.net/ficheapp/plane-a320-2088.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。截止至事故发生前，该客机机龄12年，飛行時數為6275小时。失事当天之前该飞机已执行五次航班飞行任务，分別飛到三個曾經受到恐怖攻擊或曾受到恐怖攻擊威脅的城市，第一趟是从[[厄立特里亚|厄立特里亚]][[阿斯马拉国际机场|阿斯马拉国际机场]]，飞往开罗；第二趟是从开罗飞往[[突尼西亞-迦太基國際機場|突尼西亞-迦太基國際機場]]，然后执行回程航班任務；第四次則是由开罗飞往巴黎。

== 乘客和机组 ==
804号班机机组人员尚不明确，已知的訊息包括：[[机长|机长]]有6275小时飛行經驗，其中A320为2101小时。[[副驾驶|副驾驶]]也有2766小时的飛行經驗。其他机组成员包括三名安全员与五名其他机组成员。乘客一共有56名，其中包括一名小孩与两名婴儿。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/egyptair-flight-ms804-missing-passenger-jet-has-crashed-into-the-mediterranean-sea-officials-confirm-a7037146.html |title = EgyptAir flight MS804 crash: Military searching for wreckage in Mediterranean Sea, officials say |author = Lizzie Dearden |date = 2016-05-19 |publisher = [[英國獨立報|英國獨立報]] |accessdate = 2016-05-19 |archive-date = 2016-05-20 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160520121845/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/egyptair-flight-ms804-missing-passenger-jet-has-crashed-into-the-mediterranean-sea-officials-confirm-a7037146.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>

===机组人员===
机上有10名机组人员，其中3名是机上安全员，5名是乘务员，另有两名飞行员<ref name="newyorktimes">{{cite news|last1=Walsh|first1=Declan|title=EgyptAir Plane Disappears Over Mediterranean, Airline Says|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/05/19/world/middleeast/egyptair-plane-disappears-over-mediterranean-airline-says.html?_r=0|accessdate=2016-05-19|work=[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]|date=2016-05-19|language=en-us|archive-date=2018-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181219232540/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/05/19/world/middleeast/egyptair-plane-disappears-over-mediterranean-airline-says.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据埃及航空的官方数据，執飛當次航班的機長有6,275个小时的飞行经验，其中驾驶A320机型的有2,101个小时，而副機師也有4,000小時的經驗。

