== 经过 ==
这班[[空客A320|空客A320-232R]]客机（注册编号：SU-GCC）原定于2016年5月18日20时45分在[[巴黎夏尔·戴高乐机场|巴黎夏尔·戴高乐机场]]起飞，并于第二日03时05分到达[[开罗国际机场|开罗国际机场]]<ref name ="CNN1">{{Cite web |url = http://edition.cnn.com/2016/05/18/middleeast/egyptair-flight-disappears/ |title = EgyptAir Flight 804 disappears |author = Faith Karimi and Hamdi Alkhshali |date = 2016-05-19 |publisher = [[CNN|CNN]] |accessdate = 2016-05-19 |archive-date = 2020-11-18 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201118174924/https://edition.cnn.com/2016/05/18/middleeast/egyptair-flight-disappears/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。实际在当晚09时11分离港，并于次日02时45分从[[雷达|雷达]]上消失<ref name ="CNN1"/>，飞机最后一次与[[控制塔|控制塔]]联络仅在十分钟之前。但飞机并未按照规定在进入埃及领空时向[[控制塔|控制塔]]汇报<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://edition.cnn.com/2016/05/19/middleeast/egyptair-flight-804-liveblog/ |title = EgyptAir missing plane MS804: Live updates |author1 = Nick Thompson |author2 = James Griffiths |author3 = Tiffany Ap |date = 2016-05-19 |publisher = [[CNN|CNN]] |accessdate = 2016-05-19 |archive-date = 2020-11-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201108102354/https://edition.cnn.com/2016/05/19/middleeast/egyptair-flight-804-liveblog/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。该飞机回传的最后一次[[ADS-B|ADS-B]]数据如下：
高度：11277.6公尺，速度：976.004公里/小时，航迹角：119度，经纬度：28.297447967517，33.959762573242，当地时间：2016/05/19 上午08:27:06，更新时间：2016/05/19 上午08:28:42。<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.flightradar24.com/data/aircraft/su-gcc |title = Flight history for aircraft - SU-GCC |date = 2016-05-19 |publisher = [[FlightRadar24|FlightRadar24]] |accessdate = 2016-05-19 |archive-date = 2019-08-27 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190827215505/https://www.flightradar24.com/data/aircraft/su-gcc |dead-url = no }}</ref>

该机预定在3:05着陆。埃及军方最初说，他们在4:26，即飞机从雷达上消失2小时后，收到了求救訊号。但随后他们的官员又否认了这个说法。<ref>{{cite web|title=EgyptAir flight MS804 disappears from radar between Paris and Cairo – live updates|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2016/may/19/egyptair-plane-cairo-paris-live-updates?page=with:block-573dbb67e4b04a0378340fec#block-573dbb67e4b04a0378340fec|work=The Guardian|date=2016-05-19|accessdate=2016-05-19|archive-date=2018-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181118185523/https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2016/may/19/egyptair-plane-cairo-paris-live-updates?page=with%3Ablock-573dbb67e4b04a0378340fec#block-573dbb67e4b04a0378340fec|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[希腊国防部|希腊国防部]]部长曾宣称，根据希腊军方的雷达数据，804号班机在进入埃及[[飞行情报区|飞行情报区]]后不久就转弯了。在高度37000英尺处，飞机先后向左转90度并右转360度。在此期间，飞机高度从37000英尺迅速下降至15000英尺。当飞机高度降至10000英尺后，飞机就从雷达上消失了。<ref>{{cite web |title=Π. Καμμένος: Στα 10.000 πόδια χάθηκε η εικόνα του airbus - Συνεχίζονται οι έρευνες |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nKDQyPT3dL0 |publisher=YouTube |language=el |trans_title=P. Kammenos: At 10,000 feet [was] lost the image of the Airbus - Ongoing investigation |date=2016-05-19 |accessdate=2016-05-19 |archive-date=2017-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170511104909/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nKDQyPT3dL0 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/egyptair-flight-ms804-crash-plane-swerved-suddenly-before-dropping-off-radar-over-mediterranean-sea-a7037516.html|title=EgyptAir flight MS804 crash: Plane 'swerved' suddenly before dropping off radar over Mediterranean Sea|date=2016-05-19|work=独立报|accessdate=2016-05-19|archive-date=2016-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160519114317/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/egyptair-flight-ms804-crash-plane-swerved-suddenly-before-dropping-off-radar-over-mediterranean-sea-a7037516.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>5月23日，一名来自埃及国家空中导航服务公司（National Air Navigation Services Company）的埃及民航局官员又否认了这一说法。他同时宣称，该机在坠毁前并没有改变高度，也没有做出反常动作。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-36365256|title=EgyptAir: Crashed flight MS804 'did not swerve'|publisher=[[英國廣播公司新聞頻道|BBC新聞網]]|date=2016-05-23|accessdate=2016-05-23|language=en-gb|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108100725/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-36365256|dead-url=no}}</ref>不过，埃及方面的雷达数据准确度可能不及希腊。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.utoronto.ca/news/egyptair-804-u-t-forensic-expert-explains-what-we-know-so-far|title=EgyptAir 804: U of T forensic expert explains what we know so far|last=Ahmed-Ullah|first=Noreen|date=2016-05-30|publisher=[[多伦多大学|多伦多大学]]|accessdate=2016-05-31|archive-date=2019-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191019073531/https://www.utoronto.ca/news/egyptair-804-u-t-forensic-expert-explains-what-we-know-so-far|dead-url=no}}</ref>

