==搜索和救援==
===失事海域===
埃及和希臘方面都參與了搜救行動。埃及民航部表示，[[埃及海軍|埃及海軍]]和[[希腊空军|希腊空军]]正在地中海上空的希臘空域搜尋埃及航空的失聯客機<ref name ="CNN1"/><ref name ="俄羅斯衛星網1">{{Cite web |url = http://big5.sputniknews.cn/society/20160519/1019323800.html#ixzz494q0qYOA |title = 埃希兩國空軍、埃及民航部正全力搜尋失聯客機 |date = 2016-05-19 |publisher = [[俄羅斯衛星網|俄羅斯衛星網]] |accessdate = 2016-05-19 |archive-date = 2016-06-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160625030905/http://big5.sputniknews.cn/society/20160519/1019323800.html#ixzz494q0qYOA |dead-url = no }}</ref>。另一方面，埃及空軍亦配合搜救隊從雷達屏幕上搜尋失聯客機<ref name ="俄羅斯衛星網1"/>。
希腊派出了一架[[C-130运输机|C-130运输机]]，一架EMB-145-H预警机以及一艘[[埃利级护卫舰|埃利级护卫舰]]参与搜索。<ref name="latimes">{{cite news|title=EgyptAir flight from Paris to Cairo disappears with 66 on board|url=http://www.latimes.com/world/middleeast/la-fg-egyptair-plane-20160518-snap-story.html|accessdate=2016-05-19|work=Los Angeles Times|date=2016-05-19|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204095903/https://www.latimes.com/world/middleeast/la-fg-egyptair-plane-20160518-snap-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 英国和法国也都派出舰船和飞机参与搜索。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.sky.com/story/1698511/egyptair-jet-disappears-over-mediterranean-sea|title=EgyptAir Jet Disappears Over Mediterranean Sea|accessdate=2016-05-19|date=2016-05-19|work=Sky News|archive-date=2016-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160519092250/http://news.sky.com/story/1698511/egyptair-jet-disappears-over-mediterranean-sea|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[美国海军|美国海军]]则派出一架[[P-3猎户座海上巡逻机|P-3猎户座海上巡逻机]]。
<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/05/19/middleeast/egyptair-flight-804-liveblog/index.html|title=EgyptAir missing plane MS804: Live updates|first=Nick|last=Thompson|first2=James|last2=Griffiths|first3=Tiffany|last3=Ap|work=CNN|date=2016-05-19|accessdate=2016-05-19|archive-date=2018-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180905105918/https://www.cnn.com/2016/05/19/middleeast/egyptair-flight-804-liveblog/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

5月19日，埃及官方发布消息称，距离飞机消失位置以南80公里处，[[喀帕苏斯岛|喀帕苏斯岛]]附近，发现疑似失事飞机的残骸。但埃及调查组随后确认表明，该碎片并非来自804航班<ref name="BBC36333664">{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-36333664|title=EgyptAir crash: Plane wreckage found near Greek island|date=2016-05-19|publisher=BBC新闻|accessdate=2016-05-19|language=en-GB|archive-date=2016-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160519174101/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-36333664|dead-url=no}}</ref>。埃及航空随后收回飞机残骸被找到的声明<ref name=PearsonKarimiLee>{{cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/05/18/middleeast/egyptair-flight-disappears/index.html|title=EgyptAir Flight 804: Greek official says debris not from plane, report|work=CNN|date=2016-05-19|accessdate=2016-05-19|first=Michael|last=Pearson|first2=Faith|last2=Karimi|first3=Ian|last3=Lee|archive-date=2021-01-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115191908/https://www.cnn.com/2016/05/18/middleeast/egyptair-flight-disappears/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

5月20日，{{link-en|埃及空军|Egyptian Air Force}}和[[埃及海軍|海军]]在距离[[亚历山大港|亚历山大港]]290公里的海面发现残骸，乘客遗体以及行李等私人物品。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-36339614|publisher=BBC News|date=2016-05-20|accessdate=2016-05-20|title=EgyptAir crash: 'Debris found' from flight MS804|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204161017/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-36339614|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[欧洲航天局|欧洲航天局]]声称其在航班最后发出訊号位置的东南方约40公里处（33°32′N 29°13′E）探测到一条2公里长的浮油带。该浮油于5月19日被该局的{{Le|哨兵-1A|Sentinel-1A}}型卫星探测到。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Observing_the_Earth/Copernicus/Sentinel-1/Sentinel-1A_spots_potential_oil_slick_from_missing_EgyptAir_plane|title=Sentinel-1A Spots Potential Oil Slick from Missing EgyptAir Plane|accessdate=2016-05-20|website=欧洲航天局|archive-date=2019-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190615224723/http://www.esa.int/Our_Activities/Observing_the_Earth/Copernicus/Sentinel-1/Sentinel-1A_spots_potential_oil_slick_from_missing_EgyptAir_plane|dead-url=no}}</ref>

5月22日，{{Le|埃及石油部|Ministry of Petroleum (Egypt)}}派出一艘[[遙控潛水器|遥控潜水器]]参加搜索行动。埃及总统称这艘遥控潜水器可於水下3000公尺深的地方展开工作。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-36353489 |title=EgyptAir: Submarine searches for missing flight data recorders |publisher=BBC News |date=2016-05-22 |accessdate=2016-05-22 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108114344/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-36353489 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.ctvnews.ca/world/egyptian-submarine-to-visit-plane-crash-site-1.2912555 |title=Egyptian submarine to visit plane crash site |publisher=[[CTV電視網|CTV News]] |agency=[[美聯社|美聯社]] |date=2016-05-22 |accessdate=2016-05-22}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-egyptair-airplane-idUSKCN0YD0BZ|title=Egypt sends submarine to hunt for crashed EgyptAir jet|date=2016-05-22|newspaper=[[路透社|路透社]]|accessdate=2016-05-22|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108174734/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-egyptair-airplane-idUSKCN0YD0BZ|dead-url=no}}</ref>根据[[埃及民航部|埃及民航部]]首席调查员Ayman al-Moqadem的说法，这艘遥控潜水器不能探测黑匣子发出信号。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nbc11news.com/content/news/-Signals-detected-from-EgyptAir-Flight-804-381130121.html|title=Signals detected from EgyptAir Flight 804|date=2016-05-27|work=NBC 11 News|accessdate=2016-05-27|agency=美联社|archive-date=2018-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181213134934/https://www.nbc11news.com/content/news/-Signals-detected-from-EgyptAir-Flight-804-381130121.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

5月26日，据[[CNN|CNN]]报导，卫星探测到了发自机上{{Le|紧急定位訊号发射器|Emergency Locator Transmitter}}（Emergency Locator Transmitter，下称ELT）的訊号，这个发现使调查人员将飞机主要残骸可能分布范围缩小为海床上一个直径5公里的圆形区域，也为黑盒子的搜寻工作提供了更具体的地点。<ref name="#1">{{cite news|first1=Sarah|last1=Sirgany|first2=Salma|last2=Abdelaziz|first3=Madison|last3=Park|title=Report: Signals detected from EgyptAir Flight 804 in Mediterranean|url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/05/26/middleeast/egyptair-airbus-signals-detected|publisher=CNN|date=2016-05-26|accessdate=2016-05-26|archive-date=2018-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181214220617/https://www.cnn.com/2016/05/26/middleeast/egyptair-airbus-signals-detected|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|first1=Tamer|last1=El-Ghobashy|first2=Dahlia|last2=Kholaif|first3=Robert|last3=Wall|title=Searchers Detect Emergency Signal of EgyptAir Plane|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/searchers-detect-emergency-signal-of-egyptair-plane-1464264946|newspaper=[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]|date=2016-05-26|accessdate=2016-05-26|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108103349/https://www.wsj.com/articles/searchers-detect-emergency-signal-of-egyptair-plane-1464264946|dead-url=no}}</ref>ELT可以在飞机坠海（或触地）后启动并发送紧急訊号。<ref name="#1"/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/searchers-detect-emergency-signal-of-egyptair-plane-1464264946|title=Searchers Detect Emergency Signal of EgyptAir Plane|date=2016-05-26|last2=Kholaif|first2=Dahlia|newspaper=[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]|accessdate=2016-05-26|last3=Wall|first3=Robert|first1=Tamer|last1=El-Ghobashy|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108103349/https://www.wsj.com/articles/searchers-detect-emergency-signal-of-egyptair-plane-1464264946|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|美国国家海洋和大气管理局]]称卫星在飞机失事后几分钟内接受到了这个信号。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/may/31/distress-signal-from-egyptair-flight-804-confirmed-by-authorities-in-cairo-and-us|title=Distress signal from EgyptAir flight 804 confirmed by authorities in Cairo and US|date=2016-05-31|last=|first=|publisher=卫报|accessdate=2016-06-03|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108143403/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/may/31/distress-signal-from-egyptair-flight-804-confirmed-by-authorities-in-cairo-and-us|dead-url=no}}</ref>
埃方19日报道中提到的那个在失事2小时后接收到的紧急訊号，指的可能就是ELT发出的訊号，不过，这条消息已经被埃及航空否认了。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bustle.com/articles/161783-did-egyptair-flight-ms804-send-out-a-distress-signal-there-are-mixed-reports-coming-from-egyptair |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-05-27 |archive-date=2020-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126184558/https://www.bustle.com/articles/161783-did-egyptair-flight-ms804-send-out-a-distress-signal-there-are-mixed-reports-coming-from-egyptair |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/live/egyptair-flight-missing-paris-cairo/missing-plane/|title=Distress Signal Received From Missing Plane|accessdate=2016-05-28|date=2016-05-19|last=Fahim|first=Kareem|work=纽约时报|archive-date=2018-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181213121926/https://www.nytimes.com/live/egyptair-flight-missing-paris-cairo/missing-plane/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===黑匣子===
5月20日，[[法國海軍|法国海军]]派出载有声纳设备的巡逻艇出海寻找MS804航班的黑盒子，该舰于5月23日抵达可能的坠机地点。<ref name="abcnews1">{{cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/International/egyptair-804-black-boxes-remain-unrecovered-hunt-answers/story?id=39304495|title=EgyptAir 804 Black Boxes Remain Unrecovered: What We Know About the Hunt for Answers|author=ABC News|work=ABC News|accessdate=2016-05-23|archive-date=2019-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190422055414/https://abcnews.go.com/International/egyptair-804-black-boxes-remain-unrecovered-hunt-answers/story?id=39304495|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.meretmarine.com/fr/content/disparition-du-vol-degyptair-la-marine-francaise-mobilisee |title=Disparition du vol d’EgyptAir: La marine française mobilisée |trans_title=The disappearance of the EgyptAir flight: The French Navy mobilises |website=Mer et Marine |language=fr |date=2016-05-20 |accessdate=2016-05-22 |archive-date=2020-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026011532/https://www.meretmarine.com/fr/content/disparition-du-vol-degyptair-la-marine-francaise-mobilisee |dead-url=no }}</ref>这艘法国舰艇可释放一艘可於1000公尺深的水下探测黑盒子訊号的小型潜艇。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2016/05/24/middleeast/egyptair-flight-804-main/|title=EgyptAir Flight 804: Conflicting reports over final moments|accessdate=2016-05-24|date=2016-05-24|last=Pearson|first=Michael|work=CNN|archive-date=2016-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160524184854/http://edition.cnn.com/2016/05/24/middleeast/egyptair-flight-804-main/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

5月26日，埃及政府请求部分擅长开展深水搜索作业的法国和意大利公司协助搜索失事客机的黑盒子。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/may/26/egyptair-flight-804-deep-sea-hunt-for-black-boxes-as-week-passes-since-crash|title=EgyptAir flight 804: deep-sea hunt for 'black boxes' as week passes since crash|accessdate=2016-05-26|author=Staff and agencies in Cairo|date=2016-05-26|publisher=卫报|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108142922/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/may/26/egyptair-flight-804-deep-sea-hunt-for-black-boxes-as-week-passes-since-crash|dead-url=no}}</ref>

5月27日，据BEA称，法国海军又派出一艘[[研究船|海洋探测船]]拉普拉斯号（Laplace）前往失事海域搜索。<ref>{{cite news|title=EgyptAir crash: French naval ship to join search|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-36396775|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=2016-05-27|accessdate=2016-05-27|archive-date=2019-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190526035653/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-36396775|dead-url=no}}</ref> 拉普拉斯号有望于5月30日抵达。

埃及政府已经委托{{Le|深海搜索公司|Deep Ocean Search}}的约翰·莱斯布里奇号（John Lethbridge）参与搜寻。该船装备的一艘遥控潜水器可以在6000米深的水下探测信号并勘察海床。<ref name="Reuters-Vessel-Detects"/> <ref>{{cite news|first1=Gregory|last1=Viscusi|first2=Alan|last2=Levin|first3=Andrea|last3=Rothman|title=Egypt brings in specialized deep search ship for Egyptair hunt|url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/sns-wp-blm-egyptair-025bb63e-24f1-11e6-b944-52f7b1793dae-20160528-story.html|newspaper=[[Chicago_Tribune|Chicago Tribune]]|agency=[[Bloomberg_News|Bloomberg News]]|date=2016-05-28|accessdate=2016-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160528224414/http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/sns-wp-blm-egyptair-025bb63e-24f1-11e6-b944-52f7b1793dae-20160528-story.html|archive-date=2016-05-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/05/french-vessel-joins-egyptair-black-boxes-search-160527052429526.html|title=French vessel joins EgyptAir black box search|publisher=[[Aljazeera_English|Aljazeera]]|date=2016-05-28|accessdate=2016-05-29|archive-date=2019-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190507165149/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/05/french-vessel-joins-egyptair-black-boxes-search-160527052429526.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>该船于5月28日离开[[爱尔兰海|爱尔兰海]]域，预计12天后到达，法国及埃及调查员将于[[亚历山大港|亚历山大港]]登船。<ref>{{cite news|title=EgyptAir flight MS804: Black boxes impossible to recover before 12 days, investigators say|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2016-05-30/egyptair-black-boxes-impossible-to-recover-before-12-days/7457618|publisher=[[ABC_News_(Australia)|ABC News (Australia)]]|agency=[[法新社|法新社]]|date=2016-05-30|accessdate=2016-05-30|archive-date=2017-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170112143958/http://www.abc.net.au/news/2016-05-30/egyptair-black-boxes-impossible-to-recover-before-12-days/7457618|dead-url=no}}</ref>

6月1日，埃及民航部称拉普拉斯号已经探测到黑匣子坐标定位器发出的信号。<ref name="Reuters-Vessel-Detects">{{cite news |first1=Lin |last1=Noueihed |first2=Chine |last2=Labbé |first3=Alison |last3=Williams |title=French vessel detects signals likely from EgyptAir jet black box |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-egyptair-airplane-blackboxes-idUSKCN0YN4A0 |publisher=''Reuters'' |location=Cairo |date=2016-06-01 |accessdate=2016-06-01 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108131531/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-egyptair-airplane-blackboxes-idUSKCN0YN4A0 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BBC-36427053"/>BEA也确认了这一消息，他们的发言人还说，他们已根据推测将一片海域定为优先搜索区域。<ref name="BBC-36427053">{{cite news |title=EgyptAir crash: Black box signals heard by search teams |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-36427053 |publisher=BBC News |date=2016-06-01 |accessdate=2016-06-01 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108180333/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-36427053 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

6月16日，埃及政府宣布约翰·莱斯布里奇号已经于水下13000英尺深处发现了座舱语音记录仪（CVR）。CVR部分损坏，不过存储部件依然完好。他们已将CVR送至亚历山大港。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/egyptair-crash-flight-ms804-black-box-cockpit-voice-recorder-found-mediterranean-sea-latest-a7085611.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-06-17 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108155341/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/egyptair-crash-flight-ms804-black-box-cockpit-voice-recorder-found-mediterranean-sea-latest-a7085611.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>次日，约翰·莱斯布里奇号取回了飞行数据记录器的一些部件。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-36557134 |date=2016-06-17 |accessdate=2016-06-17 |title=EgyptAir crash: Second flight recorder recovered |publisher=BBC News |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108180704/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-36557134 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 埃及民航部于6月19日宣布，在埃及军方的协助下，他们已经完成了对尚完好的存储部件的干燥并开始进行电子测试。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Gubash|first1=Charlene|last2=Gittens|first2=Hasani|title=Investigators Begin Examining EgyptAir Flight MS804 Black Boxes|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/egyptair-crash/investigators-begin-examining-egyptair-black-boxes-n595216|publisher=[[NBC_News|NBC News]]|date=2016-06-19|accessdate=2016-06-19|archive-date=2019-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713004218/https://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/egyptair-crash/investigators-begin-examining-egyptair-black-boxes-n595216|dead-url=no}}</ref> 6月21日，有官员透漏称CVR和FDR的存储部件都损坏了。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/06/21/middleeast/egyptair-data-recorders/index.html|title=EgyptAir Flight 804: Memory chips damaged|first1=Azadeh|last1=Ansari|first2=Sarah|last2=Sirgany|work=CNN|date=2016-06-21|accessdate=2016-06-22|archive-date=2020-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123200759/https://www.cnn.com/2016/06/21/middleeast/egyptair-data-recorders/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newkerala.com/news/2016/fullnews-79747.html|title=Damaged memory chips of EgyptAir Flight 804 being repaired|work=New Kerala|date=2016-06-21|accessdate=2016-06-22|archive-date=2016-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161224232131/http://www.newkerala.com/news/2016/fullnews-79747.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在下载数据的尝试失败后<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jun/24/egyptair-flight-804-access-data-recorders-information-fail- |title=EgyptAir MS804 flight recorders: efforts to extract data fail | World news |newspaper=[[卫报|卫报]] |date=2016-06-24 |accessdate=2016-06-24 |archive-date=2016-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160624030347/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jun/24/egyptair-flight-804-access-data-recorders-information-fail- |dead-url=no }}</ref>，埃及调查员于23日称他们将把黑匣子送至BEA。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-36612020 |title=EgyptAir Flight MS804 recorders to go to Paris for repairs |publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |date=2016-06-29 |accessdate=2016-06-24 |archive-date=2018-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226191032/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-36612020 |dead-url=no }}</ref>6月27日，BEA将修好的飞行数据记录仪（FDR）送回开罗进行分析。
<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-36647587|title=EgyptAir crash: Flight data recorder repaired - investigators - BBC News|work=[[BBC|BBC]]|accessdate=2016-06-28|agency=[[BBC|BBC]]|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108091028/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-36647587|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Egypt says flight 804 'black box' fixed as France opens manslaughter case|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jun/27/egyptair-flight-ms804-manslaughter-inquiry-opens|accessdate=2016-06-28|work=[[卫报|卫报]]|date=2016-06-28|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108130640/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jun/27/egyptair-flight-ms804-manslaughter-inquiry-opens|dead-url=no}}</ref>随后，修复完毕的驾驶舱语音记录也被送至开罗。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Wall|first1=Robert|title=EgyptAir Flight 804 Cockpit Recorder Successfully Repaired|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/egyptair-flight-804-cockpit-recorder-memory-chips-intact-1467461548|accessdate=2016-07-02|work=[[华尔街日报|华尔街日报]]|date=2016-07-02|archive-date=2020-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201005014351/https://www.wsj.com/articles/egyptair-flight-804-cockpit-recorder-memory-chips-intact-1467461548|dead-url=no}}</ref>

